2	
3	Issue #11 — feat: features package public API, exports, and no-key integration smoke test.
4	
5	Builds an in-memory martj42-internal-schema DataFrame (DATE/HOME_TEAM/… uppercase),
6	calls ``compute_elo`` + ``fit_dixon_coles`` once, passes both into ``build_features``
7	(historical builder) and ``wc2026_features``, then asserts:
8	  1. The two output frames share the same column set.
9	  2. The WC2026 frame's rows are a subset of the historical frame's rows.
10	
11	No network calls are made: all data is constructed in-process.
